 drivers/Kconfig         |  2 ++
 drivers/Makefile        |  3 +++
 drivers/amazon/Kconfig  | 15 +++++++++++++++
 drivers/amazon/Makefile |  3 +++
 4 files changed, 23 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/amazon/Kconfig
